deck: Phoebe has a premonition of the her own death. The Charmed ones travel to the future to stop Phoebe from dying.
name: Morality Bites

deck: Prue and Piper are trapped in a painting and only Phoebe can save them.
name: The Painted World

description: When Phil Coulson wants the heroes to report to the S.H.I.E.L.D. ice base for winter survival training, Spider-Man and his team sneak off for a vacation on a deserted tropical island that Nova found on the S.H.I.E.L.D. database. However, they soon realize that there is an inhabitant on the island who sees them as his new playmates … and does not want them to leave again.
name: Snow Day

description: While breaking into the hostile environment of TCRI headquarters, the Turtles discover the true intent of the Kraang and resolve to stop the alien invasion once and for all.
name: TCRI

description: As the Turtles try to foil a Kraang invasion plot, they are hunted by a giant, indestructible cockroach.
name: Cockroach Terminator

description: Fed up with being humiliated by Fishface and Dogpound and defeated by the Turtles, Baxter Stockman seeks revenge by luring both parties into a deadly labyrinth.
name: Baxter's Gambit

description: After witnessing the Kraang in action, Karai realizes the seriousness of the alien threat and approaches the Turtles to propose an alliance.
name: Enemy of My Enemy

description: While the Turtles are infiltrating an undersea Kraang base, the Foot Clan attempts to capture April, forcing her to fend for herself in a battle of wits against Karai.
name: Karai's Vendetta

description: When Shredder schemes to create a fearsome army of mutants, the Turtles have no choice but to rely on the help of the newest recruit to the Foot Clan: The Pulverizer!
name: The Pulverizer Returns!

description: After Leonardo, Raphael, and Donatello fall under the control of a parasitic Wasp, Michelangelo must fight his brothers to save them.
name: Parasitica

description: Donatello breaks into a secret Kraang detention center in order to rescue Kirby O'Neil. But when he discovers they are trapped inside with a deadly mutant prisoner, he realizes that breaking in was the easy part.
name: Operation: Break Out

description: As the Turtles make a desperate assault on TCRI to shut down an alien portal, they find themselves engaging in the most difficult battle yet.
name: Showdown, Part One

description: As the Turtles make a desperate assault on TCRI to shut down an alien portal, they find themselves engaging in the most difficult battle yet.
name: Showdown, Part Two

series.name: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero

description: Mesmero returns with a vengeance and switches Spider-Man’s and Hulk’s minds during a S.H.I.E.L.D. experiment. Which leads to ultimate chaos when the Thing also joins the fray.
name: The Incredible Spider-Hulk

description: Spider-Man is forced to work with Doctor Octopus when Green Goblin unleashes Venom on the S.H.I.E.L.D Helicarrier.
name: Venom Bomb

description: Spider-Man goes on a deep space adventure to save Earth from Korvac and the Chitauri. And meets the Guardians of the Galaxy.
name: Guardians of the Galaxy

description: Spider-Man and Power Man infiltrate Zodiac’s base to discover what happened to Power Man’s parents and to retrieve the Zodiac Key
name: The Parent Trap

description: Spider-Man, Mary Jane, Harry and Stan the Janitor have to descend into the sewer tunnels beneath Midtown High to track down the Lizard after he attacked Midtown High.
name: Stan By Me
Blade and the Howling Commandos Pt. 1

description: Hijacking a space shuttle, Spider-Man embarks on a mission to rescue John Jameson and clear his own name. He gets captured on Counter-Earth, a strange planet ruled by the High Evolutionary.
name: Worlds Apart, Part One

description: With the help of John Jameson and a team of freedom fighters Spider-Man escapes from his captors; only to run into a race of humanoid animals, the beastials, and deadly rivals Venom and Carnage.
name: Worlds Apart, Part two

description: Spider-Man meets the Counter Earth version of Green Goblin.
name: Where Evil Nests

description: The theft of a lethal nuclear laboratory sample forces the rebels and the beastials to team up with Spider-Man. It's a race against time to prevent the city from being blown to smithereens.
name: Deadly Choices

description: When one of the High Evolutionary's robots shows emotion, Spider-Man rescues it from the scrapheap. Mixed feelings abound as it gets caught up in a tug of war between the human rebels and the beastials.
name: Steel Cold Heart

description: Spider-Man's secret identity comes under threat when a professional human mercenary, The Hunter, is hired to take him out.
name: Enter the Hunter!

description: After a human abduction for lab experiments, the heat is on to rescue the victim as Spider-Man joins forces with The Vulture against Firedrake.
name: Cry Vulture

description: The Human Rebels enlist the help of Spider-Man in shutting down a radioactive power plant, which sparks off a clash with the shocking electro and John Jameson's alter ego Man-Wolf.
name: ill-Met by Moonlight

description: Spider-Man teams up with the Green Goblin to locate his space shuttle and head home. Can he face more rejection as a freak of nature threatens to foil his plot?
name: Sustenance

description: A dedicated human rebel searches for his long lost brother, leading to the ultimate betrayal for Spider-Man at the hands of The High Evolutionary.
name: Matters of the Heart

description: It's a grave challenge for Spider-Man when Eddie Brock is separated from his symbiote. Will Eddie Brock die or can Spider-Man hold back Carnage and re-create his toughest enemy?
name: One is the Loneliest Number

description: Spider-Man and X-51 team up to save Karen O'Mally from from High Evolutionary
name: Sins of the Fathers

description:
Final Episode

It's end game as the High Evolutionary unleashes a reign of terror to force the surrender of Spider-Man and the human rebels. The destruction of Counter-Earth looms when a strike is spawned by Venom and Carnage.
name: Destiny Unleashed

description: Caesar's Defeat! The Powerful Grizzly Magnum! (シーザー撃破! 最強の灰熊銃, Shīzā Gekiha! Saikyō no Gurizurī Magunamu)
name: Caesar's Defeat! The Powerful Grizzly Magnum!

description: As the group faces a brand new enemy, Rick and the others must fight to protect the livelihood they worked so hard to create at the prison.
name: Infected

deck: Tells the story on how Overlord Satan become Maou Sadao.
name: The Devil Arrives in Sasazuka
Black Panther vs. Juggernaut and Black Knight

description: Final episode
name: To the End

name: The Deadly Director
